Specifically, the co-founders endeavored to create and maintain a modern recording label brand to serve as a platform to promote and release the projects and recordings produced by professional artists and composers.  As experienced professionals in the field who also engage the new paradigm of the 21st Century music industry, their goal remains for the company to objectively and effectively serve as a platform for creative artists, producers and labels â€“ like themselves. Today, the Artists Recording Collective (ARC), is an independent label and established music brand name that is powered by the idea that artists need a home base for all of their music and activities.  ARC artists are reviewed in all of the top music publications worldwide. Such professional reviews are archived and cataloged at the various music portal label guides and music reference sites such as: All Music, JazzTimes, All About Jazz, etc. Association with the ARC brand serves to continually enhance the profile of member artists and labels on both, national and international levels.  ARC primarily does this by making effective and efficient use of most all relevant professional resources that are available to publicly introduce recording artists and musicians working in our innovative times.

Description: E-Fuel is a company that produce emulsified diesel fuel for heavy-duty diesel motors and Boilers. Emulsified Fuel is reliable.
Full Description: E-Fuel is a company that produce emulsified diesel fuel for heavy-duty diesel motors and Boilers. Emulsified Fuel is reliable and certified: E-Fuel is on the environment's side,  to reduce polluting emissions and the environmental impact of fuels.   *Reduction of the formation of carbon monoxide (CO) of about 90%* • Reduction of nitrogen oxides formation (NOx) of about 37% with microemulsion heaving 15% of water. Reduction of nitrogen oxides (NOx) of about 43% with microemulsion heaving 20& of water. • Reduction of carbon dioxide values (CO2) and negative products of combustion. • Total cancellation of eye-catching black smoke (particulate). • The combustion ashes are clear, dry and crumby: ashes do not adhere to the heaters surface therefore allows exchange surfaces with greater returns.  • Containment of some serious factors that negatively modify the life of the planet, causing greenhouse, acid rain, overheating.  • Approach to the provisions of the Kyoto Protocol. *Hfo emulsion is stable and can be stored in tanks and feed more Plants* • Normal water from the mains is used to create HFO EMULSION. • Reduces fuel consumption and allows savings on average between 4% - 10% compared to a traditional combustion even if well conducted.  • The improvement of combustion due to the use of HFO EMULSION is useful for the good maintenance of thermal power stations - in terms of cleanliness: reduces downtime due to cleaning cause unburnt particles are almost zero; - in terms of reduced wear: the need for replacement of filters and nozzles are reduced.  • The stability of HFO EMULSION allows its immediate use in any thermal plant already operating with bunker fuel without making any changes and without using special burners.  • Measurement carried out on pilot plants have shown an improvement of the heat generator of about 2% - 5%.  • Increasing marginality of profit on the product of about 10-15% since water is used in a big percentage instead of bunker fuel

Palisade Systems provides enterprise content security and data protection solutions.
Full Description: Palisade Systems, Inc. provides enterprise content security and data protection solutions. Its products include PacketSure, a network appliance that protects private data and controls network traffic; PacketGuard, an appliance protects various machines from unauthorized access; PacketDecoy, a device that intercepts hackers, gathers information about the intruders, and alerts about the unauthorized access; and ScreenDoor, which monitors and blocks Internet access. The company's products secure intellectual property and private client information from leaking outside the network; define and enforce access to internal network resources; and enforce compliance with federal privacy and industry security regulations. It also offers appliance installation assistance, and training services. The company serves clients in healthcare, financial services, and insurance industries, as well as universities and school districts in North America and Europe. It was formerly known as MidAmerica Networking, Inc. Palisade Systems, Inc. was founded in 1996 in Ames, Iowa and is now headquartered in Des Moines, Iowa.
Top 5 Investors: Principal Financial Group, Cedar Fund, Equity Dynamics, BP Growth Partners, John Pappajoh
